snippet.title: 'Does It Stack?' - Gameplay Trailer 1
snippet.description:
Whislist on steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2511270/Does_It_Stack/
---------------------
Do you like building epic towers with everyday objects? Then this physics-based puzzle game with an explosive twist has your name written on it. Have a taste of our diabolical challenges or be a laid-back zen master in the sandbox mode, using anything: a toaster, cheese, or mother Mary.
